r LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">.</span><a name="_ftnref20"></a><a href="#_ftn20">[20]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span></p><p style="margin:0pt 0pt 0pt 17.85pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:-17.85pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">&#xa0;</span></p><p style="margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt; font-style:normal">16.</span><span style="font:7.0pt 'Times New Roman'">&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">Fox (2013)</span><a name="_ftnref21"></a><a href="#_ftn21">[21]</a><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> postulated that with</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> better assessment, diagnosis and management of PAD in community services</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">, there</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">could be </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">fewer, but more appropriate</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> referrals to vascular clinics.</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">This</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> could in turn</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt"> free up surgical appointment slots to allow rapid access for people with critical limb </span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger LT Std 45 Light'; font-size:11pt">ischaemia</span><span style="font-family:'Frutiger